@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@apiKey = replace-with-local-api-key
@orderId = order_202605260001
@refundId = refund_202605260001_001

### Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/health/live
X-Request-Id: sample-live-001

### Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/health/ready
X-Request-Id: sample-ready-001

### Create WeChat Native payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: {{orderId}}
X-Request-Id: sample-create-wechat-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/create_wechat_native_payment.json

### Replay WeChat Native payment with same idempotency key and body
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: {{orderId}}
X-Request-Id: sample-create-wechat-replay-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/create_wechat_native_payment.json

### Query WeChat payment
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{orderId}}?provider=wechat
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
X-Request-Id: sample-query-wechat-001

### Create Alipay web payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: order_202605260002
X-Request-Id: sample-create-alipay-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/create_alipay_web_payment.json

### Query Alipay payment
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/order_202605260002?provider=alipay
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
X-Request-Id: sample-query-alipay-001

### Create WeChat refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: {{refundId}}
X-Request-Id: sample-create-refund-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/create_wechat_refund.json

### Replay WeChat refund with same idempotency key and body
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: {{refundId}}
X-Request-Id: sample-create-refund-replay-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/create_wechat_refund.json

### Query WeChat refund
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/refunds/{{refundId}}?provider=wechat
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
X-Request-Id: sample-query-refund-001

### Create Alipay refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: refund_202605260002_001
X-Request-Id: sample-create-alipay-refund-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/create_alipay_refund.json

### Query Alipay refund
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/refunds/refund_202605260002_001?provider=alipay
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
X-Request-Id: sample-query-alipay-refund-001

### Missing API key should be rejected
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/{{orderId}}?provider=wechat
X-Request-Id: sample-auth-missing-001

### Invalid zero amount should be rejected before provider call
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: invalid_amount_zero_001
X-Request-Id: sample-invalid-amount-zero-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/invalid_zero_amount_payment.json

### Invalid floating amount should be rejected before provider call
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Idempotency-Key: invalid_amount_float_001
X-Request-Id: sample-invalid-amount-float-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/invalid_float_amount_payment.json

### WeChat payment webhook with invalid placeholder signature
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/webhooks/wechat/payments
Wechatpay-Serial: invalid-placeholder
Wechatpay-Signature: invalid-placeholder
Wechatpay-Timestamp: 1779777720
Wechatpay-Nonce: invalid-placeholder
X-Request-Id: sample-wechat-webhook-invalid-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/wechat_payment_webhook_invalid_signature.json

### WeChat refund webhook with invalid placeholder signature
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/webhooks/wechat/refunds
Wechatpay-Serial: invalid-placeholder
Wechatpay-Signature: invalid-placeholder
Wechatpay-Timestamp: 1779777720
Wechatpay-Nonce: invalid-placeholder
X-Request-Id: sample-wechat-refund-webhook-invalid-001
Content-Type: application/json

< ./json/wechat_refund_webhook_invalid_signature.json

### Alipay payment webhook with invalid placeholder signature
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/webhooks/alipay/payments
X-Request-Id: sample-alipay-webhook-invalid-001
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

< ./alipay_payment_webhook_invalid_signature.form

### Alipay refund webhook with invalid placeholder signature
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/webhooks/alipay/refunds
X-Request-Id: sample-alipay-refund-webhook-invalid-001
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

< ./alipay_refund_webhook_invalid_signature.form
